{"tid":225893,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(金庸撚) 唔好再話張無忌識copy招","createTime":"2017-05-02T06:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T06:45:50.000Z","uid":2719,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25df7ccbe658c0e1bbd2ee9962e4eadfc0ea7d2f","tid":225893,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:33:18.000Z","msg":"佢只能模仿武功<br />\n無心法 點copy到？<br />\n<br />\n原理同鳩摩智一樣 得個樣<br />\n睇落去好似真係用到人地嘅武功<br />\n<br />\n但其實只係用九陽內力推動<br />\n再模仿對手動作打拳腳功夫<br />\n<br />\n根本就唔係copy <br />\n用唔到對面嘅武功<br />\n<br />\n所以啲張迷唔好成日一討論邊個好打<br />\n就話就算唔夠你打 走住屌睇你打<br />\n馬上就可以copy打返你 根本唔成立<br />\n<br />\n例如你(copy)郭靖亢龍有悔<br />\n你岀掌打岀嚟嘅都係九陽內力<br />\n唔係亢龍十八掌 明唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266643a3f442ce8b0d9488514344e1c67844e5bb","tid":225893,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:39:13.000Z","msg":"傻仔咁認真"},{"pid":"4e6808367332edf807f606ec9ba1f627ec2701e6","tid":225893,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:39:46.000Z","msg":"內輪無忌"},{"pid":"df8fa2cbda4382ef1210f5db46f3e70bc65d3d53","tid":225893,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:41:35.000Z","msg":"綠帽陽過"},{"pid":"f58ef6bcd6547183930ba820d7ae360b6779afc5","tid":225893,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:41:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>綠帽楊過</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3f467bbd5f0bbd1c9cd3c68696870281709802e7","tid":225893,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻仔咁認真</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見好多人無睇晒<br />\n正係睇過一兩部<br />\n就話楊最勁 張最勁 <br />\n唔係唔俾你覺得邊個最勁<br />\n而係你無睇晒<br />\n就唔好阻住其他人高質討論<br />\n正一識少少扮代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}